schools.name: Apple Valley Unified Preschool Special Education

data.description: Beautiful 3-Bedroom Ranch-Style Home on Huge 18,000 Square Foot Lot in Apple Valley! Upgrades on this home include vinyl plank flooring and ceiling fans throughout. Living room w/ brick fireplace. Dining area w/ sliding patio doors for al-fresco dining. Kitchen w/ granite countertops & corner pantry. Generously-sized bedrooms w/ updated bathrooms. Private fenced-in patio area – perfect for entertaining! Tesla solar system. Central AC + heat. Fully gated lot. 2 car garage w/ plenty of driveway parking. Needs a little TLC to be the perfect home!
